.IX Header "SHBias"
.IP "SHBias \-" 9
.IX Item "SHBias -"
Calculate the (cross\-)power spectrum expectation of a windowed function.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.IP "\s-1SUBROUTINE\s0 SHBias (" 20
